  <WNA_FacingVoid.stages.its_so_dark_here.description>我能感觉到的只有黑暗和虚无，这是场噩梦，我想醒过来。</WNA_FacingVoid.stages.its_so_dark_here.description>
  <!-- EN: unusually dark -->
  <WNA_FacingVoid.stages.unusually_dark.label>这里太黑了</WNA_FacingVoid.stages.unusually_dark.label>
  <!-- EN: it's so dark and empty here! I'm feeling bad! I want to wake up! -->
  <WNA_FacingVoid.stages.unusually_dark.description>这里太黑太空了！我感觉很不好，我想醒过来！</WNA_FacingVoid.stages.unusually_dark.description>
  <!-- EN: abnormally dark -->
  <WNA_FacingVoid.stages.abnormally_dark.label>异常黑暗</WNA_FacingVoid.stages.abnormally_dark.label>
  <!-- EN: it's so dark and empty here! I'm afraid! why can't I wake up? -->
  <WNA_FacingVoid.stages.abnormally_dark.description>这里太黑太空了！我很害怕！为什么我醒不过来？</WNA_FacingVoid.stages.abnormally_dark.description>
  <!-- EN: facing the void -->
  <WNA_FacingVoid.stages.facing_the_void.label>直面虚空</WNA_FacingVoid.stages.facing_the_void.label>
  <!-- EN: I can feel nothing, dark and void is all I can sense, what the hell is happening to me?! -->
  <WNA_FacingVoid.stages.facing_the_void.description>我什么都感受不到，只能感知到黑暗和虚无，我身上到底发生了什么？！</WNA_FacingVoid.stages.facing_the_void.description>
  <!-- EN: lost in the void -->
  <WNA_FacingVoid.stages.lost_in_the_void.label>迷失虚空</WNA_FacingVoid.stages.lost_in_the_void.label>
  <!-- EN: I can feel nothing, even my sense of myself is fading! I'm going to lost! -->
  <WNA_FacingVoid.stages.lost_in_the_void.description>我什么都感觉不到，就连我对自己的感知都在消失！我要消失了！</WNA_FacingVoid.stages.lost_in_the_void.description>
  <!-- EN: doomed -->
  <WNA_FacingVoid.stages.doomed.label>完了</WNA_FacingVoid.stages.doomed.label>
  <!-- EN: help! help! get me out! somebody please wake me up! I don't want to die here! -->
  <WNA_FacingVoid.stages.doomed.description>救命！救命！放我出去！有人吗！快弄醒我！我不想死在这儿！</WNA_FacingVoid.stages.doomed.description>
